Hays to Treble Staff, Expand Globally, Over Five Years, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-08T00:15:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/hays-to-treble-staff-expand-globally-over-five-years-ft-says.html
Hays Plc (HAS) , a U.K. recruitment company,
plans to treble its workforce over the next five years and open
offices in Malaysia, Columbia and  Chile , the Financial Times
reported, citing the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
